('AI Relationship Coach App', 'Mobile Apps', 'Daily check-ins, conflict resolution guidance, and communication exercises for couples. 40% divorce rate in US; 85% of couples who split cite communication as primary issue; AI mediator has scale.', '$3k–$18k MRR', '5M+/mo', '$2.8B', 74, 44, 85, 'Rising', true, ARRAY['mobile','relationships','AI','couples']),

-- ── Travel & Lifestyle ──
('AI Travel Itinerary Builder', 'Mobile Apps', 'Builds complete day-by-day travel plans from a destination and dates, with booking links. TripAdvisor has no itinerary builder; Google Trips shut down; 1.4B international travelers need planning tools.', '$4k–$24k MRR', '5M+/mo', '$4.5B', 80, 50, 88, 'Rising', false, ARRAY['mobile','travel','AI','itinerary']),
('Restaurant Discovery & Review App', 'Mobile Apps', 'AI-personalized restaurant recommendations beyond "trending" based on actual taste preferences. Yelp review manipulation is rampant; 77% of diners distrust reviews; personalization-first approach wins.', '$4k–$22k MRR', '8M+/mo', '$3.5B', 74, 55, 83, 'Rising', false, ARRAY['mobile','restaurants','AI','discovery']),
