('AI City Guide & Audio Tour App', 'Mobile Apps', 'AI-generated personalized audio tours for any city based on interests, not canned tourist scripts. Rick Steves sells static audio tours; AI generates custom tours for $4 cities in 4 seconds.', '$3k–$18k MRR', '4M+/mo', '$2.5B', 74, 44, 85, 'Rising', true, ARRAY['mobile','travel','audio-guide','AI']),

