('AI Plant Care App', 'Mobile Apps', 'Photo-identifies plants, diagnoses diseases, and sends personalized watering reminders. Plant ownership grew 60% post-COVID; 45M US plant owners kill $300 of plants/yr from neglect.', '$2k–$12k MRR', '8M+/mo', '$2.0B', 72, 46, 83, 'Rising', false, ARRAY['mobile','plants','AI','care']),
